data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Long Beach! This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is the epitome of modern comfort and convenience. Nestled in a prime location, this move-in ready abode offers the best of Long Beach living.    As you step inside, you'll be immediately struck by the warm and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept living area is bathed in natural light, creating a bright and airy ambiance. Gleaming Laminate wood floors and fresh, neutral paint throughout the house add to the sense of elegance and style.    The heart of the home is the beautifully updated kitchen, which boasts sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or enjoying a quick snack at the breakfast bar, this kitchen is a chef's delight.    The three generously sized bedrooms provide plenty of space for your family or guests. The primary suite is a true retreat, offering a private oasis with an en-suite bathroom, making it the perfect place to unwind after a long day.    One of the standout features of this property is the detached garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space. With plenty of parking options, your vehicles will always be safe and protected.    But it doesn't stop there. The expansive front yard is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts, offering endless possibilities for gardening, entertaining, or simply basking in the California sun. Imagine morning coffee on your front porch or evening gatherings with friends and family in this inviting outdoor space.    Location is key, and this home doesn't disappoint. You're just a stone's throw away from shopping centers, restaurants, and all the amenities Long Beach has to offer. Public transportation is conveniently nearby, making your daily commute a breeze.
